Go to http://vintagebus.com/howto/ for a detailed procedure on
replacing this bushing, and some other how-to's.

You don't need to drop the beam.

Tightening the steering box to fix slop is roughly equivalent to voiding 
your bladder the direction of a brisk breeze.

